License: BSD

Build depends:
* cmake
* ICU libraries
* gcc (others compilers not tested)
* zlib library (optional)
* bzlib library (optional)

Run depends:
* ICU libraries
* zlib library (optional)
* bzlib library (optional)



Unix/Linux installation from sources:
0) Download sources
1) Go to ugrep path source: cd /.../ugrep
2) Generate Makefiles: cmake . -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX:PATH=/usr/local
3) Compile: make
4) Install it: (sudo) make install
(ugrep will be installed in /usr/local/bin/ here)